thread.title: CICILY EDWARDS

author: CICILY EDWARDS
title: CICILY EDWARDS
text: I ordered the Acuvue contacts for Astigmatism for my daughter. The prices were the first thing which attracted me to Web EyeCare. This site had the cheapest prices of any other retailer that I could find. Secondly, they had her exact prescription in stock. The contacts shipped the same day that I ordered them. We received the contacts within 4 days and upon using these contacts, my daughter was very pleased. She said that she could see clearly, and did not have a need for rewetting drops! She was a happy camper and so was my purse!
